# CortexCore .gitignore
# Protege dados sensiveis. NAO ignora os ficheiros .md explicativos da estrutura,
# nem os .gitkeep necessarios para manter pastas vazias.

# --- Segredos e credenciais ---
.env
*.env
.env.*
secrets/
**/secrets/
*secret*
tokens/
*token*
credentials/
*credential*
*.key
*.pem
auth.json

# --- Bases de dados e dados privados ---
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db
private/
**/private/
*private*

# --- Uploads e exports ---
uploads/
**/uploads/
exports/
**/exports/

# --- Caches e temporarios ---
cache/
**/cache/
.cache/
tmp/
temp/
*.tmp
*.bak
*.log

# --- Obsidian (estado local / cache do workspace) ---
.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/workspace-mobile.json
.obsidian/cache/

# --- Sistema operativo ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# External project repositories
# professional/previmed/ tem .git/ proprio (repo embutido). Ignorar todo o seu conteudo.
# A ponte documental vive em professional/previmed.md (fora do repo embutido) e e versionada.
professional/previmed/

# --- VS Code workspace ---
*.code-workspace

# --- Excecoes: garantir que placeholders nao sao ignorados ---
!.gitkeep
